channel.title: Roskilde Festival
channel.description:
The Roskilde Fest is in danmark but i was wondering who all is going? I'm not until I'm 16 because it's a little weird there. But some awesome US Bands are going to be there.. Like one of my favorites: Red Hot Chili Peppers ! :)
So are you going?
You can visit the Roskilde official site @ http://www.roskilde-festival.dk
